data.description: Step inside this gently lived in home 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in Hidden Cove Frisco that perfectly blends elegance with functional living space. Impressive formal dining room & living room with gorgeous hand scraped wood floors. Start your days in this sunny spacious kitchen with beautiful windows to let in the natural light. The kitchen features plenty of storage, a breakfast area, granite counter tops, & a walk-in pantry. Split Master suite down with garden tub, dual vanities, separate shower & huge walk-in closet. Walk-in closets in all bedrooms. Play ball in this HUGE back yard with privacy fence. Lots of space for pets to run. Lots of storage. Two attic & two linen closets! Book a private showing NOW!
